    "body": "Spark RAPIDS plugin increasingly relies on state machine abstractions implicitly and explicitly in recent designs such as retry framework. To improve reliability, this issue proposes to use TLA+ to specify the state machines and model check them for safety properties and liveness / deadlock freedom properties.\r\n  \r\n```[tasklist]\r\n### Tasks\r\n- [ ] Create a toy example state machine and familize oneself with the ecosystem\r\n- [ ] Extract the state machine for the memory allocation rety framework\r\n- [ ] TBD next task\r\n```\r\n",
